      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis is mechanically flawless, having received a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul to ensure peak reliability. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and communicative feedback inherent to the M-chassis. All electronics and climate control systems function within factory parameters. This is a turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
